{"tid":2069810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐議會5黨轟北京全面攻擊港自治 動議設港人「救生艇」","createTime":"2020-06-18T16:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:17:10.000Z","uid":60281,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b0df503ea7ed340acef228cd752f7df2b57cab59","tid":2069810,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"到歐洲出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為歐盟主要決策機構之一的「歐洲議會（European Parliament）」，在香港時間今日（18日）下午3時開會，並就一項題為「關於港區國安法及歐盟捍衞香港高度自治的必要性」的動議展開辯論。議案由包括議會第二大黨「社會民主進步聯盟（S&amp;D Group）」在內、共5個黨團代表及多名議員提出，並動議歐盟在人權情況持續惡化下，為香港市民提供「救生艇計劃（lifeboat scheme）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200618/7VUT7LBADJLA32GARIVFJ6KJVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2F7VUT7LBADJLA32GARIVFJ6KJVI%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHrPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=394bbf48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2F7VUT7LBADJLA32GARIVFJ6KJVI%2F&h=797d6084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200618/7VUT7LBADJLA32GARIVFJ6KJVI/</a>"},{"pid":"ce88be0a09d41b940d3cc6af321764249beaef6c","tid":2069810,"uid":182222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"聽住先<br />\n歐盟D嘢都係唔好跟車太貼"},{"pid":"a6bcba7a75a04724e980feea97449696c72927de","tid":2069810,"uid":276715,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"有英美澳加幫嘅話 其實無咩人會去歐盟國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ada3ad5bdb77a10dbe8231ca6d636fc5616d0f7","tid":2069810,"uid":90521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a6bcba7a75a04724e980feea97449696c72927de","tid":2069810,"uid":276715,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"有英美澳加幫嘅話 其實無咩人會去歐盟國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\